This paper is likely to belong to the sub-category of cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it discusses the use of deep learning models and their optimization. It also falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision) as it mentions the use of these models in computer vision tasks. Additionally, it could be categorized under cs.AR (Hardware Architecture) as it discusses the challenges of deploying these models on low power and mobile devices. It also falls under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) as it discusses the use of deep learning models in natural language processing. Finally, it could be categorized under cs.SY (Systems and Control) as it discusses the optimization of deep learning operators for multiple CPU architectures.
